Package gdt.jgui.console

Contains basic graphic components and structures for building java swing user interface.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JContext
    This interface defines a context.
    JFacetRenderer
    This interface defines the facet renderer functionality.
    JRequester
    This interface describes the requester functionality.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JClipboard
    This class contains methods to support the application's clipboard.
    JClipboardPanel
    This context contains a list of clipboard items.
    JConsoleHandler
    This class serves as a dispatcher for creating different contexts.
    JConsoleHandler.TitleComparator  
    JFacetAddItem
    This class represents an item in the list of facets available for adding to an entity.
    JFacetOpenItem
    This class represents a facet assigned to the entity.
    JItemPanel
    This class represents the general-purpose graphical item in the list console.
    JItemsListPanel
    This abstract class is a super class for list consoles which contains instances of the JItemPanel class.
    JItemsListPanel.ItemPanelComparator  
    JMainConsole
    This is the main application console.
    JTrackPanel
    This class displays the list of previously shown contexts.
